law.history: Repealed, effective March 23, 1998, 1996 Ky. Acts ch. 365, sec. 64, effective upon contingency; contingent effective date repealed 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 101, sec. 20, effective March 23, 1998. -- Amended 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 74, Art. VI, sec. 107(19). -- Amended 1972 Ky. Acts ch. 158, sec. 10. -- Created 1954 Ky. Acts ch. 190, sec. 16, effective July 1, 1954.

metadata.lrc-note: (7/15/98). Under KRS 446.260, the repeal of this section in 1996 Ky. Acts ch. 365 prevails over its amendment in 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 426.
